    Closeable
    Deprecated. 
    Only for reading old 4.0 segments

    @Deprecated
public class Lucene40SkipListReader
extends MultiLevelSkipListReader
    Implements the skip list reader for the 4.0 posting list format that stores positions and payloads.
    See Also:
